cube = Cube((3, 3, 3))
for action in parse_actions("RUR'U'"):
    action.perform(cube, Orientation())
match = cube.orient(Orientation(), keeping=Side.LEFT, bottom=Pattern([[
    Color.WHITE, None, None], [None, None, None], [None, None, None]]))
assert Orientation(Side.FRONT, Side.TOP) == match
